        "text": "I wouldn't be surprised that in the near future agentic IDEs will contextualize error messages and express them in terms of the user's intent. Then the challenge becomes ensuring that LLMs can translate R concepts correctly, and the efforts of this group would shift towards high quality glossaries and examples that agents can consume. Curious what others think.",
